INSTALL GUIDE AND USER GUIDE
7.1 INSTALLATION GUIDE
7.1.1 System Requirements

Laptop/Desktop with webcam

Node.js v18+

Modern browser (Chrome/Edge)

Internet connection

7.1.2 Software Requirements

Node.js

npm / yarn

Git

7.1.3 Installation Steps
git clone https://github.com/Yashmax-cmd/tryon-live-style.git
cd tryon-live-style
npm install
npm start


Open browser and navigate to:
http://localhost:3000

7.1.4 Configuration

Allow webcam permissions

Ensure shirt assets are placed in /assets

Backend API URL configured in .env

7.1.5 Troubleshooting
Issue	Solution
Webcam not loading	Check browser permissions
Shirt not aligning	Ensure good lighting
App not starting	Reinstall node modules
